{
  "stem": "13981.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they had subdelegations, like the French had-- I mean, the Russian had, for instance, had the Yugoslav, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and so forth, and wherever the-- but they were part of the Russian prosecution staff.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- Justice Jackson.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ex-senator, Dodd, whose son is senator also in, in Connecticut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oh, yes, there was a fellow by the name of-- he handled Rosenberg's case.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Well, it'll come back to me after a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Colonel Petrovski, with whom I worked quite a bit and have a story to tell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Colonel Petrovski and I had a wonderful working relationship.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So nothing personal ever happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he spoke German fluently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all our business was actually transacted in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when my contract was up, it was just a few weeks before the trials ended.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my contract was not renewed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wanted show him how much I had appreciated our working relationship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went and bought him a Parker pencil-- pen and pencil set.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to his office and started to talk German and tell him the reason for my coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I handed him this little gift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And suddenly, he switched from speaking German into speaking Russian through an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he-- and, and I, of course, switched to English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he told something to his interpreter-- secretary interpreter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she left the room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a few minutes later, she came back with two volumes of evidence that actually had been presented in court just a few weeks earlier.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he autographed one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then he told me, Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
